Kostadis Roussos: She says these meetings are used to clear the end of the year before Dead Winter Day. Dead Winter Day is, like, the end of year celebration in Erun. It's kind of like New Year's Eve kind of thing.

768
01:01:35.600 --> 01:01:37.600
Kostadis Roussos: Right.

769
01:01:38.120 --> 01:01:47.990
Kostadis Roussos: At least half of the talks this year seemed to have ended in EXPLOSIVE shatting matches. I do hate gossip, but if it's necessary for the investigation…

770
01:01:50.370 --> 01:01:54.209
Kostadis Roussos: This is where you're supposed to say it's necessary for the investigation? You all get…

