01:06:02.980 --> 01:06:05.640
Kostadis Roussos: The last time, the rung before long.

815
01:06:06.140 --> 01:06:09.400
Kostadis Roussos: I, I, and, and I thought I heard a thud upstairs.

816
01:06:10.240 --> 01:06:14.940
Kostadis Roussos: I would have gone to investigate, but Janusi doesn't likes to be disturbed after 11PM.

817
01:06:16.710 --> 01:06:20.609
