821
01:06:38.970 --> 01:06:39.310
Kostadis Roussos: Yes.

822
01:06:39.310 --> 01:06:39.990
Joe Beda: Yeah, but…

823
01:06:39.990 --> 01:06:43.279
Kostadis Roussos: True goes, oh, yes, yes, yes, yes, he was very much alive.

824
01:06:44.080 --> 01:06:44.780
Ben Pfaff: How did…

825
01:06:44.780 --> 01:06:49.189
