827
01:06:55.350 --> 01:07:05.159
Kostadis Roussos: Yeah, well, I never go to sleep before 11 o'clock, because the Master Genusi might want something, you never know, and at 11 o'clock is when I finally close my eyes and go to bed.

828
01:07:05.670 --> 01:07:08.780
Ben Pfaff: How does she know that he was still alive?

829
01:07:09.840 --> 01:07:15.589
Kostadis Roussos: Well, he makes noises, and, you know, there's always some… he's a very fussy man.

830
01:07:15.590 --> 01:07:17.239
Ben Pfaff: Oh, okay, so…

831
01:07:17.240 --> 01:07:18.559
Joe Beda: Nothing more.

832
01:07:18.560 --> 01:07:28.070
Kostadis Roussos: And she starts crying. Congratulations. Congratulations, Thorin, you're gonna now have to roll a, you know, some kind of,

833
01:07:28.070 --> 01:07:29.959
Joe Beda: Where's my empathy skill?

834
01:07:29.960 --> 01:07:31.019
Kostadis Roussos: persuasion check.

835
01:07:31.020 --> 01:07:32.329
Joe Beda: Empathy minus 5.

836
01:07:35.080 --> 01:07:35.760
Kostadis Roussos: Oh.

837
01:07:35.760 --> 01:07:38.959
Daz: I rolled a NAT 20, by the way, on the insight check.

838
01:07:39.110 --> 01:07:39.800
