839
01:07:39.800 --> 01:07:41.970
Joe Beda: I mean, so, I'm an asshole, but…

840
01:07:42.270 --> 01:07:43.510
Joe Beda: Not that much of an asshole.

841
01:07:43.510 --> 01:07:44.690
Ben Pfaff: I've got 15 also.

842
01:07:45.820 --> 01:07:47.109
Gabe: You're muted, Gustavis.

843
01:07:47.110 --> 01:07:55.290
Kostadis Roussos: Sorry. So, Daz is, of course, paying no attention to this, you know, crying woman, right? I mean, the three of you have managed to calm her down.

844
01:07:56.070 --> 01:07:59.079
Kostadis Roussos: Thorin, that was very much on brand.

845
01:08:05.070 --> 01:08:15.860
Kostadis Roussos: So, so first though, so first of all, the reason she knew he wasn't dead was because he makes noises until he goes to bed, and so she…

846
01:08:16.350 --> 01:08:20.200
Kostadis Roussos: She never goes to sleep until after he's gone to bed, and so…

847
01:08:21.490 --> 01:08:25.689
Kostadis Roussos: She was reasonably confident he was awake till then, and then she went to bed, and then she heard the thump.

848
01:08:26.879 --> 01:08:27.789
Joe Beda: Alright, so I wonder.

849
01:08:27.790 --> 01:08:29.499
Kostadis Roussos: Hold on, hold on, before you do that, before you do that…

