01:08:29.500 --> 01:08:31.910
Joe Beda: I just want to add this to the stack, by the way.

851
01:08:31.910 --> 01:08:35.050
Kostadis Roussos: So, you remembered…

852
01:08:36.109 --> 01:08:43.010
Kostadis Roussos: a prophecy that was cited by Alwando. So Aluando's one of those guys who keeps producing prophecies.

853
01:08:44.779 --> 01:08:45.460
Kostadis Roussos: Alright.

