856
01:09:01.330 --> 01:09:03.329
Joe Beda: Is this, like, some Nostradamus bullshit, or are these things.

857
01:09:03.330 --> 01:09:07.170
Kostadis Roussos: Yeah, no, these are… well, so it's not Nostradamus because they happen to be real.

858
01:09:07.520 --> 01:09:07.930
Joe Beda: Okay.

859
01:09:07.939 --> 01:09:08.519
