860
01:09:08.520 --> 01:09:13.590
Joe Beda: But Nostradamus-like figure, but, like, in this world, people can actually predict the future.

861
01:09:13.590 --> 01:09:14.380
Kostadis Roussos: Yes.

862
01:09:14.380 --> 01:09:15.929
