867
01:09:30.960 --> 01:09:37.270
Kostadis Roussos: Yeah, yeah, I just need to find it so that I don't,

868
01:09:38.500 --> 01:09:44.509
Kostadis Roussos: Alright, I have it, I have it, I have it carefully selected so that I don't have to spend the next 20 minutes looking for it.

869
01:09:44.990 --> 01:09:47.430
Kostadis Roussos: And of course, now when I need it, I can't find it, right?

